        'meta_title' => 'The Vigan Empanada Trail: Three Stalls, One Orange Pastry | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A 90-minute Vigan empanada trail through three Plaza Burgos stalls with notes on annatto shell, longganisa, papaya filling, and the cracked-egg method.',
        'tags' => 'Vigan, Empanada, Food Trail, Ilocos Sur, Heritage',
