        'meta_title' => 'Burnayan Pottery in Vigan: A Heritage Craft Deep-Dive | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A heritage workshop visit to the Pagburnayan burnay jar makers in Vigan with notes on clay mixing, foot-pedal wheel throwing, and rice husk kiln firing.',
