        'meta_title' => 'Taal Heritage Town Walk in Batangas | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A half-day Taal heritage town walk in Batangas covering the Basilica, Casa Villavicencio, Casa Agoncillo, embroidery row, and tapang Taal stalls.',
        'tags' => 'Batangas, Taal, Heritage, Walking Tour, Bahay na Bato',
