        'meta_description' => 'A heritage walking guide to Silay in Negros Occidental covering Balay Negrense, Hofileña House, Jalandoni Pink House, El Ideal Bakery, and Cinco de Noviembre Street.',
        'tags' => 'Negros, Silay, Heritage, Walking Tour, Bacolod',
