        'meta_title' => 'Sinulog in Cebu: A Festival Deep-Dive | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A festival deep-dive on Sinulog in Cebu every third Sunday of January with notes on the Santo Niño, the dance step, novena masses, fluvial procession, and grand parade.',
